	Mabel: You can take the first bus back
	Player: I'm kidding 😂
Mabel: Thought: Okay everything's set up
Mabel: Thought: Snacks, movies, pillows...
Mabel: Thought: I hope the perfume isn't too much
Mabel: Hey so uhm
Mabel: Since it's just the two of us tonight 👉👈
Mabel: Do you wanna maybe...
Mabel: Practice... y'know 😶
Mabel: Maybe.. 😚🙈
Mabel: Thought: Why is this so hard to say when we've already done it
Mabel: I just want tonight to feel... special? 🙈
- I'll make sure it does 😘
	Player: I'll make sure it does 😘
	Mabel: PinkThought: My chest feels so warm right now
	Mabel: You better 🥰
- You're already making it special
	Player: You're already making it special
	Mabel: Stoooop 😭
	Mabel: You can't say stuff like that when I'm already this nervous
Player: Of course 😚
Mabel: img: mabel/140
Mabel: PinkThought: I want him to hold me tonight
Mabel: Well hurry..
Mabel: I can't wait omg
Player: 🫠
Player: I just reached
Mabel: 🥰
Mabel: Thought: Deep breaths Mabel
Mabel: Thought: It's just your boyfriend staying the night
Mabel: PinkThought: ...just your boyfriend staying the night
